        },
        "product_description": {
            "value": "Is your child obsessed with Star Wars and the Mandalorian? This UFO ball hovering helicopter toy is a perfect gift idea this holiday season! The mini helicopter features one of everyone’s favorite characters from the hit Disney franchise - Darth Vader!\r\n\r\nMade with solid and durable materials, this helicopter toy is also super-lightweight, so no worrying about it breaking anything after a rough landing. It features a coaxial rotor system to provide hovering stability and precise movements (with 2 spare rotors included).\r\n\r\nThis Star Wars UFO copter uses infrared motion-sensing technology to detect nearby objects and will automatically dodge them, preventing in-flight damage. It also comes with a convenient USB charger so you can charge it just about anywhere.\r\n\r\nThe mini copters are super easy for kids to use too - just charge it, turn it on, and have them hold their hand underneath it to keep it hovering. Once done with playtime, just grab it out of the air carefully or use any IR remote control to shut it down safely. Your little Star Wars fanatic is sure to love this toy copter!",
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "usurper",
